---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Psychiatric Rehabilitation (PRP)">
  <div class="container" style="padding: var(--spacing-6) 0;">
    
    <nav aria-label="Breadcrumbs" style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4);">
      <a href="/">Home</a> &gt; <a href="/programs/">Programs</a> &gt; <span aria-current="page">PRP Program</span>
    </nav>
    <header style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-6);">
      <h1 style="font-size: 2.5rem; color: var(--color-primary-blue);">Psychiatric Rehabilitation Program (PRP)</h1>
      <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--color-text-muted);">Skill-building and resource management for managing mental health barriers effectively.</p>
    </header>
    <div class="grid" style="grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr; gap: var(--spacing-6);">
      <div class="main-content">
        <section style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-5);">
          <h2>What the Service Is</h2>
          <p>Our PRP service assists adults in developing, enhancing, and retaining psychiatric stability, social competencies, personal adjustment, and independent living competencies. We provide life skills training, community integration, and personalized development strategies.</p>
        </section>
        <section style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-5);">
          <h2>Who It Is For</h2>
          <p>The program is intended for adults and adolescents who face challenges with severe and persistent mental illness and require support transitioning into community settings or maintaining current community living statuses.</p>
        </section>
        <section style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-5);">
          <h2>How to Qualify</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Currently engaging in outpatient mental health treatment (seeing a therapist or psychiatrist regularly).</li>
            <li>Referred by a licensed mental health professional.</li>
            <li>Eligible under Maryland Medical Assistance guidelines.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>
        <section style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-5);">
          <h2>What Happens Next</h2>
          <p>After an intake form is received, an assigned PRP coordinator will review the referral within <strong>3 business days</strong> and schedule an assessment to outline rehabilitation goals.</p>
        </section>
      </div>
      <aside>
        <div class="card" style="background-color: var(--color-bg-offset); border-top: 4px solid var(--color-accent-gold);">
          <h3>Take the First Step</h3>
          <p style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4);">Secure your spot and start your evaluation online to expedite the process.</p>
          <a href="/intake/start/" class="btn" style="display: block; width: 100%; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2);">Start Your Intake</a>
          <a href="/referral/start/" class="btn btn-secondary" style="display: block; width: 100%;">Providers: Refer a Client</a>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
